    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "问题背景"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "BYD RTC:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Bug 1821996: [Stability][PCS04][中科版本]偶现开机后'/usr/bin/displaydiag'进程未启动 - Change and Configuration Management (bosch.com)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Bug 1866442: [Stability][PCS04][中科版本]偶现开机后'/usr/bin/displaydiag'进程未启动 - Change and Configuration Management (bosch.com)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "GEELY RTC:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "1883143: [G636][SOP]【台架】【开关机压测】fusa重启导致开机两次"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "问题描述："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "在开关机压测的过程中，发现fusa displaydiag以及signature-unit-controller进程有极低的概率（<1/2000）不能被PRD启动脚本拉起来，进程未运行"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "查看串口日志如下："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "[PUTTYRX] - [TRACE] - secpolgenerate: displaydiag (pid:1642587 uid:2032 type:displaydiag_t) failed to access /dev/mq/inc_dispatcher/sih_inc_message (/dev/mq/inc_dispatcher/sih_inc_message"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "[ERROR][45]displaydiag - SUMMARY: pid:1642587 terminated, reason: CLD_EXITED - Child has exited, errno:0, exit status:1 [ERROR][45]displaydiag - terminated() - unexpected termination of app"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "第一行是说security模块检测到我们进程无权限访问节点/dev/mq/inc_dispatcher/sih_inc_message，打印的原因是由于我们进程起来时要去open这个节点"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "第二行是说我们这个进程在被PRD启动脚本拉起来时在main执行时主动return了-1，而导致进程未正常运行"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/16_SOC%20fusa%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E5%81%B6%E5%B0%94%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5/image-2023-9-8_10-58-21.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/16_SOC fusa进程偶尔拉不起来/image-2023-9-8_10-58-21.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/16_SOC%20fusa%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E5%81%B6%E5%B0%94%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5/image-2023-9-8_10-58-52.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/16_SOC fusa进程偶尔拉不起来/image-2023-9-8_10-58-52.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "在如上两个函数中加printf日志后（slog日志在return时不打印），复现得到如下日志："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Line  812: 20230821 00:45:31.070200 - [PUTTYRX] - [TRACE] - [sm52inc_dispatcher]mq open failed 13, /inc_dispatcher/sih_suc_message"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Line  799: 20230821 00:45:30.870193 - [PUTTYRX] - [TRACE] - [signatureisplaydiag (pid:3575929 uid:2032 type:displaydiag_t) failed to access /dev/mq/inc_dispatcher/sih_inc_message (/dev/mq/inc_dispatcher/sih_inc_message Line  813: 20230821 00:45:31.085694 - [PUTTYRX] - [TRACE] - [displaydiag]failed to open /inc_dispatcher/sih_suc_message"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "证实了：确实是displaydiag没有对/dev/mq/inc_dispatcher/sih_inc_message节点的访问能力而造成了进程异常终止"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "分析："
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/16_SOC%20fusa%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E5%81%B6%E5%B0%94%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5/image-2023-9-8_11-5-22.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/16_SOC fusa进程偶尔拉不起来/image-2023-9-8_11-5-22.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/16_SOC%20fusa%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E5%81%B6%E5%B0%94%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5/image-2023-9-8_11-5-39.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/16_SOC fusa进程偶尔拉不起来/image-2023-9-8_11-5-39.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/16_SOC%20fusa%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E5%81%B6%E5%B0%94%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5/image-2023-9-8_11-5-59.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/16_SOC fusa进程偶尔拉不起来/image-2023-9-8_11-5-59.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "如上的启动脚本所述，displaydiag要启动首先要setfacl_inc_dispatcher_sih_inc_message1满足返回值为true，而setfacl_inc_dispatcher_sih_inc_message1要运行依赖于waitfor_diag_sih_inc_message以及__SLM_SM52IncDispatcher_pathname_tmp_sync_sm52inc-dispatcher的成立"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "__SLM_SM52IncDispatcher_pathname_tmp_sync_sm52inc-dispatcher为inc-dispatcher建的同步点，waitfor_diag_sih_inc_message为对这条message节点真实存在的检查"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "说明在setfacl_inc_dispatcher_sih_inc_message1运行时是满足/dev/mq/inc_dispatcher/sih_inc_message节点真实存在的要求的，因为如果不加这两条依赖的话，setfacl_inc_dispatcher_sih_inc_message1的运行就可能会对一个虚假不存在（尚未建立）的节点去设置权限，如果这种情况发生，那么程序可能不能正常运行"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "回到问题，即使加了这么严格的条件去执行setfacl -m u:pj_displaydiag:r /dev/mq/inc_dispatcher/sih_inc_message，但最终程序被执行时仍然报failed to access，故问题诊断为setfacl未能成功给节点设置权限导致，但为啥setfacl失败了仍能执行进程呢，这里我试了下，即使给一个虚假的节点设置setfacl，但setfacl后仍然能返回true，说明setfacl内部有bug，这更能加强我对setfacl本身无法正常设置权限这一故障的确信"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "诊断："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "问题大致被分类为启动脚本在执行setfacl给节点设置权限时未能成功"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "解决方案："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "setfacl为DAC中ACL的运用，目的是扩展节点能被访问的访问者的list，如果不设置ACL，那么节点只能被创建者相同的uid和gid的进程所访问，例如："
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/16_SOC%20fusa%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E5%81%B6%E5%B0%94%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5/image-2023-9-8_11-21-41.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/16_SOC fusa进程偶尔拉不起来/image-2023-9-8_11-21-41.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "这些节点创建者的uid和gid是 pj_sm52inc_dispatcher（2023），而节点的权限组是rwxrwx---，也就是相同uid和gid进程对它的访问能力是rwx，而其它用户对它的访问能力是—，就是完全无任何权限，也就是pj_displaydiag（2032）如果要访问它，那么必须使用setfacl去帮助pj_displaydiag拥有对这个节点的访问能力，而setfacl被证明有bug，有的时候不能设置成功。解决思路是：将pj_displaydiag加入pj_sm52inc_dispatcher的用户组（gid），让pj_displaydiag直接默认持有对这个节点的访问能力，跳过了setfacl的使用，修改的PRD文件如下："
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/16_SOC%20fusa%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E5%81%B6%E5%B0%94%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5/image-2023-9-8_11-28-14.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/16_SOC fusa进程偶尔拉不起来/image-2023-9-8_11-28-14.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/16_SOC%20fusa%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E5%81%B6%E5%B0%94%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5/image-2023-9-8_11-28-31.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/16_SOC fusa进程偶尔拉不起来/image-2023-9-8_11-28-31.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "displaydiag运行的条件简化为只检查这个节点是否存在，一旦节点存在，直接就执行进程，同时将进程加到pj_sm52inc_dispatcher的gid中，运行pidin u产看displaydiag的属性如下："
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/16_SOC%20fusa%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E5%81%B6%E5%B0%94%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5/image-2023-9-8_11-31-27.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/16_SOC fusa进程偶尔拉不起来/image-2023-9-8_11-31-27.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/16_SOC%20fusa%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E5%81%B6%E5%B0%94%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5/image-2023-9-8_11-31-10.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/16_SOC fusa进程偶尔拉不起来/image-2023-9-8_11-31-10.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "说明displaydiag持有了对这些节点的访问了，跳过了setfacl"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "压测结果："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "无复现"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "解决状态"
    },
